    WHERE `c`.`catmaster_id` = @__catmasterId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS `t`
LEFT JOIN `cost_master` AS `c0` ON `t`.`catmaster_id` = `c0`.`catmaster_id`
LEFT JOIN `departure_date_master` AS `d` ON `t`.`catmaster_id` = `d`.`catmaster_id`
LEFT JOIN `itinerary_master` AS `i` ON `t`.`catmaster_id` = `i`.`catmaster_id`
LEFT JOIN `tour_master` AS `t0` ON `t`.`catmaster_id` = `t0`.`catmaster_id`
ORDER BY `t`.`catmaster_id`, `c0`.`cost_id`, `d`.`departure_date_id`, `i`.`itinerary_id`

    SELECT `c`.`catmaster_id`, `c`.`category_id`, `c`.`flag`, `c`.`image_path`, `c`.`name`, `c`.`subcategory_id`
    FROM `category_master` AS `c`
    WHERE `c`.`catmaster_id` = @__catmasterId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS `t`
LEFT JOIN `cost_master` AS `c0` ON `t`.`catmaster_id` = `c0`.`catmaster_id`
LEFT JOIN `departure_date_master` AS `d` ON `t`.`catmaster_id` = `d`.`catmaster_id`
LEFT JOIN `itinerary_master` AS `i` ON `t`.`catmaster_id` = `i`.`catmaster_id`
LEFT JOIN `tour_master` AS `t0` ON `t`.`catmaster_id` = `t0`.`catmaster_id`
ORDER BY `t`.`catmaster_id`, `c0`.`cost_id`, `d`.`departure_date_id`, `i`.`itinerary_id`

SELECT `t`.`catmaster_id`, `t`.`category_id`, `t`.`flag`, `t`.`image_path`, `t`.`name`, `t`.`subcategory_id`, `c0`.`cost_id`, `c0`.`base_cost`, `c0`.`catmaster_id`, `c0`.`child_with_bed_cost`, `c0`.`child_without_bed_cost`, `c0`.`extra_person_cost`, `c0`.`single_person_cost`, `c0`.`valid_from_date`, `c0`.`valid_to_date`, `d`.`departure_date_id`, `d`.`catmaster_id`, `d`.`departure_date`, `d`.`end_date`, `d`.`number_of_days`, `i`.`itinerary_id`, `i`.`catmaster_id`, `i`.`day_number`, `i`.`itinerary_details`, `t0`.`tour_id`, `t0`.`catmaster_id`, `t0`.`departure_date_id`, `t0`.`description`
FROM (
    SELECT `c`.`catmaster_id`, `c`.`category_id`, `c`.`flag`, `c`.`image_path`, `c`.`name`, `c`.`subcategory_id`
    FROM `category_master` AS `c`
    WHERE `c`.`catmaster_id` = @__catmasterId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS `t`
LEFT JOIN `cost_master` AS `c0` ON `t`.`catmaster_id` = `c0`.`catmaster_id`
LEFT JOIN `departure_date_master` AS `d` ON `t`.`catmaster_id` = `d`.`catmaster_id`
LEFT JOIN `itinerary_master` AS `i` ON `t`.`catmaster_id` = `i`.`catmaster_id`
LEFT JOIN `tour_master` AS `t0` ON `t`.`catmaster_id` = `t0`.`catmaster_id`
ORDER BY `t`.`catmaster_id`, `c0`.`cost_id`, `d`.`departure_date_id`, `i`.`itinerary_id`
2026-02-05 12:04:19.749 +05:30 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[@__catmasterId_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

    SELECT `c`.`catmaster_id`, `c`.`category_id`, `c`.`flag`, `c`.`image_path`, `c`.`name`, `c`.`subcategory_id`
    FROM `category_master` AS `c`
    WHERE `c`.`catmaster_id` = @__catmasterId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS `t`
LEFT JOIN `cost_master` AS `c0` ON `t`.`catmaster_id` = `c0`.`catmaster_id`
LEFT JOIN `departure_date_master` AS `d` ON `t`.`catmaster_id` = `d`.`catmaster_id`
LEFT JOIN `itinerary_master` AS `i` ON `t`.`catmaster_id` = `i`.`catmaster_id`

SELECT `t`.`catmaster_id`, `t`.`category_id`, `t`.`flag`, `t`.`image_path`, `t`.`name`, `t`.`subcategory_id`, `c0`.`cost_id`, `c0`.`base_cost`, `c0`.`catmaster_id`, `c0`.`child_with_bed_cost`, `c0`.`child_without_bed_cost`, `c0`.`extra_person_cost`, `c0`.`single_person_cost`, `c0`.`valid_from_date`, `c0`.`valid_to_date`, `d`.`departure_date_id`, `d`.`catmaster_id`, `d`.`departure_date`, `d`.`end_date`, `d`.`number_of_days`, `i`.`itinerary_id`, `i`.`catmaster_id`, `i`.`day_number`, `i`.`itinerary_details`, `t0`.`tour_id`, `t0`.`catmaster_id`, `t0`.`departure_date_id`, `t0`.`description`
FROM (
    SELECT `c`.`catmaster_id`, `c`.`category_id`, `c`.`flag`, `c`.`image_path`, `c`.`name`, `c`.`subcategory_id`
    FROM `category_master` AS `c`
    WHERE `c`.`catmaster_id` = @__catmasterId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS `t`
LEFT JOIN `cost_master` AS `c0` ON `t`.`catmaster_id` = `c0`.`catmaster_id`
LEFT JOIN `departure_date_master` AS `d` ON `t`.`catmaster_id` = `d`.`catmaster_id`
LEFT JOIN `itinerary_master` AS `i` ON `t`.`catmaster_id` = `i`.`catmaster_id`
LEFT JOIN `tour_master` AS `t0` ON `t`.`catmaster_id` = `t0`.`catmaster_id`
ORDER BY `t`.`catmaster_id`, `c0`.`cost_id`, `d`.`departure_date_id`, `i`.`itinerary_id`

    SELECT `b`.`booking_id`, `b`.`booking_date`, `b`.`booking_status`, `b`.`customer_id`, `b`.`departure_date_id`, `b`.`tax_amount`, `b`.`total_amount`, `b`.`total_passengers`, `b`.`tour_amount`, `b`.`tour_id`, `c`.`customer_id` AS `customer_id0`, `c`.`address`, `c`.`city`, `c`.`email`, `c`.`mobile_number`, `c`.`name`, `c`.`password`, `c`.`reset_password_token`, `c`.`reset_password_token_expiry`, `c`.`role`, `c`.`state`, `t`.`tour_id` AS `tour_id0`, `t`.`catmaster_id`, `t`.`departure_date_id` AS `departure_date_id0`, `t`.`description`, `c0`.`catmaster_id` AS `catmaster_id0`, `c0`.`category_id`, `c0`.`flag`, `c0`.`image_path`, `c0`.`name` AS `name0`, `c0`.`subcategory_id`, `d`.`departure_date_id` AS `departure_date_id1`, `d`.`catmaster_id` AS `catmaster_id1`, `d`.`departure_date`, `d`.`end_date`, `d`.`number_of_days`
    FROM `booking_header` AS `b`
    INNER JOIN `customer_master` AS `c` ON `b`.`customer_id` = `c`.`customer_id`
    INNER JOIN `tour_master` AS `t` ON `b`.`tour_id` = `t`.`tour_id`
    INNER JOIN `category_master` AS `c0` ON `t`.`catmaster_id` = `c0`.`catmaster_id`
    INNER JOIN `departure_date_master` AS `d` ON `b`.`departure_date_id` = `d`.`departure_date_id`
    WHERE `b`.`booking_id` = @__bookingId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS `t0`
LEFT JOIN `passenger_master` AS `p` ON `t0`.`booking_id` = `p`.`booking_id`
LEFT JOIN `payment` AS `p0` ON `t0`.`booking_id` = `p0`.`booking_id`
ORDER BY `t0`.`booking_id`, `t0`.`customer_id0`, `t0`.`tour_id0`, `t0`.`catmaster_id0`, `t0`.`departure_date_id1`, `p`.`passenger_id`

    SELECT `c`.`catmaster_id`, `c`.`category_id`, `c`.`flag`, `c`.`image_path`, `c`.`name`, `c`.`subcategory_id`

    WHERE `c`.`catmaster_id` = @__catmasterId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS `t`
